l was trying to stop it.

1162
01:28:33,968 --> 01:28:35,760
Well, there it goes again.

1163
01:28:52,993 --> 01:28:55,236
You're all confused, aren't you?

1164
01:28:56,957 --> 01:28:58,618
-Aren't you?
-No.

1165
01:28:58,876 --> 01:29:01,629
