You mean that, Jerry?

1174
01:29:21,365 --> 01:29:22,741
Are you sure?

1175
01:29:23,076 --> 01:29:26,446
No more doubts? No more being....

1176
01:29:29,292 --> 01:29:31,333
-Except....
-Except what?

1177
01:29:31,879 --> 01:29:34,881
-There's only one thing that bothers me.
-What?

1178
01:29:37,387 --> 01:29:38,965
